{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/3133/comments/133110116.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/3133/_/diff#comment-133110116"}}, "parent": {"id": 133109772, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/3133/comments/133109772.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/3133/_/diff#comment-133109772"}}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 3133, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/pullrequests/3133.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/pull-requests/3133"}}, "title": "Support SDFormat 1.7 frame semantics"}, "content": {"raw": "This works inside `<model>` though, just not inside `<include>`:\n\n```\n<?xml version=\"1.0\"?>\n<sdf version=\"1.7\">\n  <world name=\"default\">\n    <frame name=\"F_I\">\n      <pose>5 0 0 0 0 0</pose>\n    </frame>\n    <include>\n      <pose relative_to=\"F_I\"> 0 5 0.4 0 0 0</pose>\n      <uri>model://number1</uri>\n    </include>\n    <model name=\"M\">\n      <static>true</static>\n      <pose relative_to=\"F_I\"> 0 5 0.4 0 0 0</pose>\n      <link name=\"L\">\n        <visual name=\"V\">\n          <geometry>\n            <sphere>\n              <radius>0.5</radius>\n            </sphere>\n          </geometry>\n        </visual>\n      </link>\n    </model>\n  </world>\n</sdf>\n```\n\n![relative_to.png](data/bitbucket.org/repo/jgXqbo/images/3597364966-relative_to.png)", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>This works inside <code>&lt;model&gt;</code> though, just not inside <code>&lt;include&gt;</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"cp\">&lt;?xml version=&quot;1.0&quot;?&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"nt\">&lt;sdf</span> <span class=\"na\">version=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;1.7&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;world</span> <span class=\"na\">name=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;default&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>\n